[14:07:02] {"event": "tool_result", "tool": "bash", "is_error": false, "result": {"status": "success", "stdout": "# Instructions\n\n- Following Playwright test failed.\n- Explain why, be concise, respect Playwright best practices.\n- Provide a snippet of code with the fix, if possible.\n\n# Test info\n\n- Name: home-page.spec.ts >> TC-83232 — Newsletter signup in footer accepts valid email and redirects to confirmation @newsletter @footer\n- Location: tests/home-page.spec.ts:399:5\n\n# Error details\n\n```\nTimeoutError: page.waitForURL: Timeout 45000ms exceeded.\n=========================== logs =========================\n... [output truncated] ...\n       - /url: /\n          - img \"London Drugs\" [ref=e28]\n        - generic [ref=e31]:\n          - textbox \"Search for products\" [ref=e32]:\n            - /placeholder: Find your product\n          - img [ref=e33] [cursor=pointer]\n        - complementary [ref=e35]:\n          - list [ref=e36]:\n            - listitem [ref=e37]:\n              - link \"Select Your Store\" [ref=e38] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /stores\n                - img [ref=e39]\n                - text: Select Your Store", "stderr": ""}}
