[14:08:33] {"event": "tool_call", "tool": "think", "args": {"thought": "\nThe \"SIGN UP\" button is covered by a `div` with class `mx-auto hidden max-w-[1272px] flex-row items-center justify-between px-2 py-3 lg`. This is a nav/layout div, not an anchor tag. The button IS there and visible but a div is on top of it.\n\nUsing `force: true` on the button click should bypass the overlay and click the button directly. This is the appropriate fix for Edge.\n\nLet me also check:\n- The `check_visibility` earlier said it's covered by `<a>` - but that was on the email INPUT, not the button\n- The button is covered by a `div` (the header perhaps?)\n\nActually wait - looking at the position: after scrolling to the bottom, the button should be visible and near the bottom. But there's a `div` covering it. On Edge, Playwright's click action would fail because it would try to click the covering div instead of the button.\n\nUsing `force: true` bypasses the actionability check and clicks the element directly regardless of coverage. This should fix the Edge issue.\n\nLet me update the test to use `{ force: true }` on the newsletter submit button click.\n"}}
[14:08:39] {"event": "tool_call", "tool": "edit", "args": {"file_path": "/Users/virginia.zambudio/PlaywrightAutomation/tests/home-page.spec.ts", "old_string": "        await test.step('Click SIGN UP button', async () => {\n            await homePage.newsletterSubmitButton.waitFor({ state: 'visible', timeout: 30_000 });\n            await homePage.newsletterSubmitButton.click();\n        });", "new_string": "        await test.step('Click SIGN UP button', async () => {\n            await homePage.newsletterSubmitButton.waitFor({ state: 'visible', timeout: 30_000 });\n            // The newsletter section can have an overlapping layout element on some browsers\n            // (e.g. Edge). Use force:true to bypass the actionability overlay check and\n            // dispatch the click event directly to the button element.\n            await homePage.newsletterSubmitButton.click({ force: true });\n        });"}}
